OL,3,CMan shot dead during suspected
OL,4,Cburglary 'had heart of gold'
OL,6,FA man who was shot dead during a
OL,7,Fsuspected burglary has been described
OL,8,Fby his family as having a "heart of
OL,9,Fgold" as three men appeared in court
OL,10,Fin connection with the incident.
OL,12,FConnor Batty, 26, of Barnsley, was
OL,13,Ffound dead at the rear of a property
OL,14,Fon Barnsley Road in Hemsworth on
OL,15,FThursday, 11 September.
OL,17,FWest Yorkshire Police said the
OL,18,Fincident happened after three men
OL,19,Fforced entry to the property at about
OL,20,F9.30pm.
