OL,3,CMan shot dead during suspected
OL,4,Cburglary 'had heart of gold'
OL,6,FIn a statement, Mr Batty's family
OL,7,Fsaid: "Connor was a brother, father,
OL,8,Fpartner and uncle. He was loved dearly
OL,9,Fby all his family and was a loyal kind
OL,10,Fperson with a heart of gold.
OL,12,F"He has lost life and now as a family
OL,13,Fwe are having to deal with this and
OL,14,Fwould like people to respect our
OL,15,Fprivacy in our grief.
OL,17,F"We understand that there is a lot of
OL,18,Fspeculation and a number of comments
OL,19,Fare being made online but ask people
OL,20,Fto refrain on commenting until they
OL,21,Fknow the full circumstances."
