OL,3,CMan shot dead during suspected
OL,4,Cburglary 'had heart of gold'
OL,6,FAdrian Frost, 60, from Hemsworth, was
OL,7,Finitially arrested on suspicion of Mr
OL,8,FBatty's murder, but appeared before
OL,9,Fmagistrates on Monday charged with
OL,10,Fpossession of a firearm and production
OL,11,Fof class B drugs.
OL,13,FHe was remanded in custody to appear
OL,14,Fbefore Leeds Crown Court on 13 October.
OL,16,FPolice said the murder investigation
OL,17,Fremains ongoing.
