OL,6,FDylan Kelly, 23, of Locksley Gardens,
OL,7,FBarnsley, and Lewis Bromley, 25, of
OL,8,FRose Avenue, Barnsley, appeared at
OL,9,FBradford Magistrate's Court charged
OL,10,Fwith aggravated burglary and having a
OL,11,Ffirearm with intent to commit an
OL,12,Findictable offence.
OL,14,FThey were both remanded in custody to
OL,15,Fappear before Bradford Crown Court on
OL,16,F15 October.
